OL,3,CClawed hammers wielded by pupil were
OL,4,C'tools, not weapons', Blundell's head
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe full letter said: "Dear Blundell's
OL,8,FCommunity, The trial ended today with
OL,9,FGuilty verdicts on all three counts of
OL,10,Fattempted murder and I wanted to write
OL,11,Fto you with our immediate response.
OL,13,F"It concludes a challenging year and I
OL,14,Fhope that this outcome will bring a
OL,15,Fdegree of closure for all those
OL,16,Finvolved.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
